在[[化學|化學]]中，'''氮3'''（Trinitrogen）又稱為'''疊氮自由基'''，是[[氮|氮]]的[[同素異形體|同素異形體]]。

==性質==
氮3的每個[[分子|分子]]具有三個氮原子，直鏈和環狀的結構皆是可能的，<ref name=han>{{cite journal |last1=Hansen |first1=N. |last2=Wodtke |first2=A. M. |title=Velocity Map Ion Imaging of Chlorine Azide Photolysis:  Evidence for Photolytic Production of Cyclic-N3 |journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry A |date=December 2003 |volume=107 |issue=49 |pages=10608–10614 |doi=10.1021/jp0303319|bibcode=2003JPCA..10710608H }}</ref>但都極不穩定。更為穩定的衍生物是存在的，例如作為[[配體|配體]]時，可能在[[疊氮化鈉|疊氮化鈉]]與[[硝酸鈰銨|硝酸鈰銨]]出現疊氮硝化合成反應時出現等。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Schlegel |first1=H. Bernhard |last2=Skancke |first2=Anne |title=Thermochemistry, energy comparisons, and conformational analysis of hydrazine, triazane, and triaminoammonia |journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society |date=August 1993 |volume=115 |issue=16 |pages=7465–7471 |doi=10.1021/ja00069a053}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |doi=10.1007/b59072|title=Inorganic Molecules|volume=25A|series=Landolt-Börnstein - Group II Molecules and Radicals|year=1998|isbn=3-540-61713-2}}</ref>

其直鏈結構首次於1956年由布萊恩·特魯什發現，<ref name="jin">{{cite journal |last1=Jin |first1=Lin |last2=Yu |first2=Xue-fang |last3=Pang |first3=Jing-lin |last4=Zhang |first4=Shao-wen |last5=Ding |first5=Yi-hong |title=Theoretical Study on the Reactions of the Cyclic Trinitrogen Radical toward Oxygen and Water |journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry A |date=30 July 2009 |volume=113 |issue=30 |pages=8500–8505 |doi=10.1021/jp810741v|bibcode=2009JPCA..113.8500J }}</ref>他當時對[[疊氮酸|疊氮酸]]進行[[光分解作用|光分解作用]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Thrush |first1=B. A. |title=The Detection of Free Radicals in the High Intensity Photolysis of Hydrogen Azide |journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society A: Mathematical, Physical and Engineering Sciences |date=10 April 1956 |volume=235 |issue=1200 |pages=143–147 |doi=10.1098/rspa.1956.0071|bibcode=1956RSPSA.235..143T }}</ref>其環狀結構在2003由Nils Hansen及Alec Wodtke取得，他們對[[疊氮化氯|疊氮化氯]]進行紫外光分解，得到的氮3大部分為直鏈，但有約兩成為環狀。<ref name="jin"/><ref name=han/>

直鏈狀氮3的分子結構具有D<sub>∞h</sub>的二面體群對稱性、其平均鍵長為1.8115 Å；第一個激发态A<sup>2</sup>Σ<sub>u</sub>的能量比基態高約4.56[[電子伏特|電子伏特]]。<ref name=han/>

